g.text: MOTIVATIONSDaniel loves to save images he finds online for inspiration. He’s bookmarked hundreds overthe course of 3 years. However, the browser can just be slightly frustrating. Creating folders,managing them, etc. It’s sometimes overwhelming and should be easier. He wants tocollaborate with others on his team to share what he finds with ease. Subscribes to severalsoftware applications, and never can remember passwords. Would love something thatcombines a few of those.

text.tspan: sing on his phone during the 30­-minu

g.text: “If I had a way to share inspiration with my team, we could save time from meeting constantly.”
